snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Kiss at the  2015 Toronto International Film Festival
snippet.description: Johnny Depp poses with his wife Amber Heard while stepping out for the premiere of The Danish Girl held during the 2015 Toronto International Film Festival at the Princess of Wales Theatre on Saturday (September 12) in Toronto, Canada. The couple was joined on the red carpet by Eddie Redmayne and his wife Hannah Bagshawe, as well as Alicia Vikander.
